content:
The first step in decision optimization is to select the model to optimize recommendations for. In Model Manager, models are organized by prediction definitions.

In Analytics Studio, go to Model Manager and click Optimize Click the Select Model step, and select the prediction definition that contains the model that you want to optimize the recommendations for.

Selecting a prediction definition simultaneously selects the Einstein Discovery model and the Salesforce object where you want to see the optimized recommendations.

Click Next.
title: Selecting a Model for Decision Optimization in Salesforce
